                        </svg>
                    </a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </header>
    <main class="main-content">
        <div class="hero-section">
                <img src="https://discoverycove.com/orlando/-/media/discovery-cove-orlando/images/attractions/included/dolphin-swim/2021/banner/1900x630-dco-dolphinlagoon.ashx?version=1_202104143331" alt="">
        </div>

        <section class="m-section">
            <div class="m-section-container">
                <div class="m-section-wrapper">
                    <article class="m-article article-1">
                        <h2>BOOK WITH CONFIDENCE</h2>
                        <p>
                            We understand you’re looking for flexibility in your vacation planning. That’s why we’ve enhanced our booking policy, so you
                            can easily shift reservations you've made, up to 48 hours prior to your reservation date.
                        </p>
                    </article>
                    <div class="form-section">
                        <form  name="addBooking" action="/booknow/booknow" method="post" >
                            <input type="hidden" name="hotel" id="hotel" value="1">
                            <input type="hidden" name="tourCompany" id="tourCompany" value="2">
                            <div class="form-group fg-1">
                                <div class="form-group-set">
                                    <label for="adults">Adults</label>
                                    <input type="number" name="adults" id="adults" min="0" value="0">
                                </div>
                                <div class="form-group-set">
                                    <label for="infants">Infants</label>
                                    <input type="number" name="infants" id="infants" min="0" value="0">
                                </div>
                                <div class="form-group-set fg-fill">
                                    <label for="programs">Programs</label>
                                    <select name="programs" id="programs" required>
                                        <option selected disabled></option>
                                        <%
                                        for(i=0 ; i < programs.length; i++) { %>
                                            <option value="<%=programs[i].id%>"><%=programs[i].program%></option>
                                            <% }
                                                                                 
                                            
                                        %>
                                    </select>
                                </div>
                                <div class="form-group-set fg-fill">
                                    <label for="exc_date">Excursion Date</label>
                                    <input type="date" name="exc_date" id="exc_date" required>
                                </div>
                                <div class="form-group-set fg-fill">
                                    <label for="shedule">Shedule</label>
                                    <select name="shedule" id="shedule" required>
                                        <option selected disabled></option>
                                        <%
                                        for(i=0 ; i < shedule.length; i++) { %>
                                            <option value="<%=shedule[i].id %>"><%=shedule[i].shedule %></option>
                                            <% }
                                                                                 
                                            
                                        %>
                                    </select>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="form-group fg-1">
  


                            </div>
                            <div class="form-sub-header">
                                <span>Contact Information</span>
                            </div>
                            <div class="form-group fg-1">
                                <div class="form-group-set fg-fill">
                                    <label for="fname">First Name</label>
                                    <input type="text" name="fname" id="fname" required>
                                </div>
                                <div class="form-group-set fg-fill">
                                    <label for="lname">Last Name</label>
                                    <input type="text" name="lname" id="lname" required>
                                </div>
                                <div class="form-group-set fg-fill">
                                    <label for="email">Email</label>
                                    <input type="email" name="email" id="email" required>
                                </div>
                                <div class="form-group-set fg-fill">
                                    <label for="cell">Cell</label>
                                    <input type="text" name="cell" id="cell" required>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="form-sub-header">
                                <span>Payment Information</span>
                            </div>
                            <div class="form-group fg-1">
                                <div class="form-group-set">
                                    <label>Payment Type</label>
                                    <div class="radio-group">
                                        <%
                                        for(i=0 ; i < ptype.length; i++) { %>
                                            <div>
                                                <input type="radio" id="ptype" name="ptype" value="<%=ptype[i].id%>" required>
                                                <label for="ptype"><%=ptype[i].payment_type%></label>
                                            </div>
    
                                            <% }
                                        %>
                                    </div>
    
                                </div>
                                <div class="form-group-set">
                                    <label>Payment Status</label>
                                    <div class="radio-group">
                                        <%
                                        for(i=0 ; i < pstatus.length; i++) { %>
                                            <div>
                                                <input type="radio" id="pstatus" name="pstatus" value="<%=pstatus[i].id%>" required>
                                                <label for="pstatus"><%=pstatus[i].status%></label>
                                            </div>
    
                                            <% }
                                        %>
                                    </div>
    
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="submit-section">
                                <div class="controls">
                                    <button type="submit">Book Now</button>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </form>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>
        <section class="m-section">
                <div class="m-section-wrapper">
                    <article class="m-article article-1">
                        <img src="https://www.dolphincoveja.com/Content/src/cards.png" alt="">
                    </article>
                </div>
        </section>
        <section class="m-section m-section-footer">
            <div class="m-section-container">
                <div class="m-section-wrapper">
                    <div class="social-section">
                        <div class="social-header">
                            <span>STAY CONNECTED</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="social-img">
                            <ul>
                                <li>
                                    <img src="https://discoverycove.com/orlando/-/media/images/social/fb.ashx?version=1_201806250826&h=52&w=53&la=en&hash=061A8006A717E44B66D574BE40BD9A5CA7A09580" alt="">
                                </li>
                                <li>
                                    <img src="https://discoverycove.com/orlando/-/media/images/social/instagram.ashx?version=1_201808094504&h=52&w=53&la=en&hash=2F65F9EBF67EC04D741F38E45473914CC2EA44E5" alt="">
                                </li>
                                <li>
                                    <img src="https://discoverycove.com/orlando/-/media/images/social/youtube.ashx?version=1_202107084202&h=52&w=53&la=en&hash=76F054F502925C6607880D2D96C1FBD2B5851A13" alt="">
                                </li>
                                <li>
                                    <img src="https://discoverycove.com/orlando/-/media/images/social/email.ashx?version=1_201808031629&h=52&w=53&la=en&hash=4FF02EC740BDFB9FCCFDCD7116DEFC5B13AFD6EA" alt="">
                                </li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>
                        <div class="social-text">
                            <p>Follow us for real-time updates on what’s happening at Dolphin Cove.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>
    </main>
    <footer class="site-footer">
        <div class="footer-container">
            <div class="footer-wrapper">
                <div class="copyright">
                    <p>© 2022 Dolphin Cove</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </footer>
</body>
</html>